keyMappings:
# Ctrl key
map <c-n> scrollDown
map <c-p> scrollUp
map <c-s> enterFindMode
map <c-P> togglePinTab
map <c-m> toggleMuteTab

# Command mode
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight

# Search engines
map z Vomnibar.activate keyword=bizuuid
map Z Vomnibar.activate keyword=bizid
map a Vomnibar.activate keyword=aduuid
map A Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=afbizuuid
searchEngines:
# Work searches
bizuuid: http://admin.austin.ownlocal.com/businesses?query=%s [MP] Business UUID:
aduuid: http://admin.austin.ownlocal.com/publishers/1/ads/%s [MP] Ad UUID:
bizid: http://admin.austin.ownlocal.com/businesses/%s [MP] Business Short ID:
afbizuuid: http://adforge.ownlocal.com/admin/businesses/%s [AF] Business UUID:

# Others
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
gm: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google maps
